{{version031}}
{{flavour|Empowers the magic of nearby wizard allies of the caster, allowing them to cast their magic more powerfully and more often.}}

'''Aura of Brilliance''' affects nearby allies of the caster who have the [[Spell slot flags|Wizard flag]] on their spells. Affected creatures are more likely to cast spells, and their spells are cast as if they had 5 extra [[HD]], resulting in more damage, higher chance of success, and so forth.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
{{CBA|0.32|this spell will be renamed to '''Prayer of Brilliance''' and changed into a one-time buff.}}

[[Category:Monster spells]]
